1
00:00:01,669 --> 00:00:03,960
<Default><b>[♪ Solemn
orchestral music]</b></Default>

2
00:00:14,080 --> 00:00:15,120
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

3
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:18,855
<Default><b>{\i1}I mean, after all</b></Default>

4
00:00:18,879 --> 00:00:22,129
<Default><b>{\i1}it's thanks to Master Naofumi{\i0}
{\i1}that I'm even alive right now.{\i0}</b></Default>

5
00:00:22,500 --> 00:00:23,805
<Default><b>{\i1}Yeah, that's right.{\i0}</b></Default>

6
00:00:23,829 --> 00:00:25,949
<Default><b>{\i1}Atla was getting sicker{\i0}
{\i1}by the day.{\i0}</b></Default>

7
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,560
<Default><b>{\i1}She never would've recovered{\i0}
{\i1}without his help.{\i0}</b></Default>

8
00:00:28,750 --> 00:00:29,790
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

9
00:00:30,329 --> 00:00:32,305
<Default><b>[MIRELIA] I figured I'd
find you here.</b></Default>

10
00:00:32,329 --> 00:00:33,369
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

11
00:00:35,380 --> 00:00:37,460
<Default><b>How have the children
been faring?</b></Default>

12
00:00:37,750 --> 00:00:39,510
<Default><b>The white
tiger siblings.</b></Default>

13
00:00:40,250 --> 00:00:42,039
<Default><b>Last I heard</b></Default>

14
00:00:42,130 --> 00:00:44,330
<Default><b>accompanying
the Shield Hero's party.</b></Default>

15
00:00:44,630 --> 00:00:45,670
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

16
00:00:45,960 --> 00:00:48,120
<Default><b>You mean to tell me
you let them go?</b></Default>

17
00:00:48,420 --> 00:00:49,820
<Default><b>And to Siltvelt?</b></Default>

18
00:00:50,250 --> 00:00:52,050
<Default><b>Their kind is
hated there.</b></Default>

19
00:00:53,710 --> 00:00:57,880
<Default><b>[war sound, screams]</b></Default>

20
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,290
<Default><b>{\i1}Magic Prism!{\i0}</b></Default>

21
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:06,679
<Default><b>[magical charging sound]</b></Default>

22
00:01:07,079 --> 00:01:08,396
<Default><b>{\i1}Now's our chance!{\i0}</b></Default>

23
00:01:08,420 --> 00:01:09,860
<Default><b>{\i1}Give it your all!{\i0}</b></Default>

24
00:01:10,209 --> 00:01:11,959
<Default><b>{\i1}Drifa Shine Ray!{\i0}</b></Default>

25
00:01:12,040 --> 00:01:13,760
<Default><b>[magical charging sound]</b></Default>

26
00:01:14,079 --> 00:01:16,379
<Default><b>[♪ Angelical chorus]</b></Default>

27
00:01:18,500 --> 00:01:19,629
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

28
00:01:23,879 --> 00:01:26,209
<Default><b>[roars]</b></Default>

29
00:01:30,709 --> 00:01:33,750
<Default><b>[♪ Gentle music]</b></Default>

30
00:01:34,459 --> 00:01:37,019
<Default><b>[AULTCRAY] In my nation's
war against Siltvelt</b></Default>

31
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:40,726
<Default><b>countless
lives were lost.</b></Default>

32
00:01:40,750 --> 00:01:43,110
<Default><b>And one of them
was their leader, Tyrant.</b></Default>

33
00:01:46,579 --> 00:01:50,290
<Default><b>The white tigers were forced
to bear full responsibility</b></Default>

34
00:01:50,629 --> 00:01:53,269
<Default><b>and lost any position
they had in their country.</b></Default>

35
00:01:55,629 --> 00:01:57,079
<Default><b>Those poor kids.</b></Default>

36
00:01:57,170 --> 00:01:59,726
<Default><b>They carry with them
the burden of Tyrant's blood.</b></Default>

37
00:01:59,750 --> 00:02:01,950
<Default><b>Siltvelt doesn't take
kindly to that.</b></Default>

38
00:02:02,379 --> 00:02:05,226
<Default><b>Yes, but those children have
their own path to follow.</b></Default>

39
00:02:05,250 --> 00:02:05,790
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

40
00:02:05,879 --> 00:02:06,879
<Default><b>But...</b></Default>

41
00:02:10,789 --> 00:02:13,580
<Default><b>Need I remind you</b></Default>

42
00:02:14,379 --> 00:02:17,580
<Default><b>I have every confidence
he'll ensure their safety.</b></Default>

43
00:02:18,669 --> 00:02:19,709
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

44
00:02:30,039 --> 00:02:32,519
<Default><b>I'm not listening to another
second of this!</b></Default>

45
00:02:33,830 --> 00:02:34,830
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

46
00:02:35,379 --> 00:02:37,669
<Default><b>[♪ Opening music begins]</b></Default>

47
00:02:42,580 --> 00:02:46,169
<Default><b>THE RISING OF
THE SHIELD HERO</b></Default>

48
00:04:03,629 --> 00:04:05,830
<Default><b>[♪ opening music ends]</b></Default>

49
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:07,605
<Default><b>[♪ Tense, playful music]</b></Default>

50
00:04:07,629 --> 00:04:09,379
<Default><b>EPISODE 3: A TRUE PEOPLE</b></Default>

51
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:12,390
<Default><b>[MAN] That white tiger needs
to be put in place.</b></Default>

52
00:04:12,830 --> 00:04:13,870
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

53
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,160
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

54
00:04:16,379 --> 00:04:18,739
<Default><b>[JARALIS] The girl
carries tainted blood.</b></Default>

55
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,320
<Default><b>What? But how?</b></Default>

56
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:24,040
<Default><b>Do you mean to tell us this girl
bears human blood?</b></Default>

57
00:04:24,540 --> 00:04:26,355
<Default><b>Could it be
she's Tyrant's?</b></Default>

58
00:04:26,379 --> 00:04:27,170
<Default><b>Look, brat.</b></Default>

59
00:04:27,329 --> 00:04:29,579
<Default><b>You have no right to
speak amongst us.</b></Default>

60
00:04:29,670 --> 00:04:31,110
<Default><b>Be gone with you.</b></Default>

61
00:04:32,540 --> 00:04:34,329
<Default><b>Bears tainted blood.</b></Default>

62
00:04:34,540 --> 00:04:36,020
<Default><b>No right to speak?</b></Default>

63
00:04:36,379 --> 00:04:37,579
<Default><b>How absurd.</b></Default>

64
00:04:38,379 --> 00:04:41,099
<Default><b>How could you say such a thing
after poisoning us?</b></Default>

65
00:04:41,329 --> 00:04:43,289
<Default><b>Your accusation
means nothing.</b></Default>

66
00:04:43,579 --> 00:04:45,146
<Default><b>The citizens of Siltvelt</b></Default>

67
00:04:45,170 --> 00:04:46,435
<Default><b>and especially you.</b></Default>

68
00:04:46,459 --> 00:04:47,896
<Default><b>[JARALIS] Hold
your tongue!</b></Default>

69
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,160
<Default><b>This nation…</b></Default>

70
00:04:49,709 --> 00:04:53,000
<Default><b>Has forgotten the one thing
that still unites it as one.</b></Default>

71
00:04:53,709 --> 00:04:55,349
<Default><b>If I were to stop here</b></Default>

72
00:04:55,379 --> 00:04:57,699
<Default><b>I would never be able
to forgive myself.</b></Default>

73
00:04:58,209 --> 00:04:59,209
<Default><b>Atla…</b></Default>

74
00:04:59,709 --> 00:05:02,516
<Default><b>As Master Naofumi's shield
who's sworn to protect him</b></Default>

75
00:05:02,540 --> 00:05:03,555
<Default><b>you're wrong!</b></Default>

76
00:05:03,579 --> 00:05:06,059
<Default><b>I declare all of you
to be completely wrong!</b></Default>

77
00:05:06,709 --> 00:05:08,000
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

78
00:05:08,079 --> 00:05:09,129
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

79
00:05:09,959 --> 00:05:12,879
<Default><b>[JARALIS] And how exactly
are we the ones in the wrong?</b></Default>

80
00:05:13,420 --> 00:05:16,040
<Default><b>For starters</b></Default>

81
00:05:16,129 --> 00:05:18,305
<Default><b>are disrespectful
to the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

82
00:05:18,329 --> 00:05:19,646
<Default><b>[LADY] You
take that back.</b></Default>

83
00:05:19,670 --> 00:05:22,030
<Default><b>[MAN] We would never
disrespect our Hero.</b></Default>

84
00:05:22,459 --> 00:05:24,709
<Default><b>Ever since he arrived</b></Default>

85
00:05:24,790 --> 00:05:27,590
<Default><b>within our power to welcome him
here with open arms.</b></Default>

86
00:05:27,629 --> 00:05:30,476
<Default><b>If that's true, then why have
you continued to deny him</b></Default>

87
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:32,396
<Default><b>his very simple request
for a ship?</b></Default>

88
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:33,000
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

89
00:05:33,290 --> 00:05:35,805
<Default><b>Even worse, your behavior
towards him has been</b></Default>

90
00:05:35,829 --> 00:05:38,170
<Default><b>disrespectful since
we arrived here.</b></Default>

91
00:05:38,329 --> 00:05:40,250
<Default><b>It's disturbing</b></Default>

92
00:05:40,329 --> 00:05:42,105
<Default><b>But the worst part
about all of it</b></Default>

93
00:05:42,129 --> 00:05:44,266
<Default><b>is that it took me
so long to realize</b></Default>

94
00:05:44,290 --> 00:05:46,250
<Default><b>how rude all
of you were being.</b></Default>

95
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:49,379
<Default><b>Now then, I have
a question for you.</b></Default>

96
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:52,829
<Default><b>How was Siltvelt founded
in the first place?</b></Default>

97
00:05:53,420 --> 00:05:54,040
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

98
00:05:54,379 --> 00:05:55,379
<Default><b>[sigh]</b></Default>

99
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:58,790
<Default><b>I believe it was the Shield Hero
who made it possible</b></Default>

100
00:05:58,879 --> 00:06:01,709
<Default><b>for Demi-humans and beast men
to live side by side.</b></Default>

101
00:06:01,959 --> 00:06:02,976
<Default><b>Correct.</b></Default>

102
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,305
<Default><b>And in the same way</b></Default>

103
00:06:04,329 --> 00:06:07,049
<Default><b>Master Naofumi's gone
and founded his own village.</b></Default>

104
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,920
<Default><b>It's like
Lurolona Village.</b></Default>

105
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,480
<Default><b>I'm welcome there.</b></Default>

106
00:06:12,379 --> 00:06:15,290
<Default><b>[♪ Gentle,
emotional music]</b></Default>

107
00:06:27,829 --> 00:06:29,629
<Default><b>Well, we are
still slaves.</b></Default>

108
00:06:29,670 --> 00:06:30,750
<Default><b>You see?</b></Default>

109
00:06:31,629 --> 00:06:35,129
<Default><b>Master Naofumi welcomed beast men
and Demi-humans alike</b></Default>

110
00:06:35,379 --> 00:06:37,305
<Default><b>giving them not just
a place to live</b></Default>

111
00:06:37,329 --> 00:06:39,750
<Default><b>but a place they can
finally call home.</b></Default>

112
00:06:40,379 --> 00:06:42,500
<Default><b>All of us are forever
in his debt.</b></Default>

113
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:46,290
<Default><b>Not only do I serve him</b></Default>

114
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:47,790
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

115
00:06:47,879 --> 00:06:49,679
<Default><b>We all should
be thankful.</b></Default>

116
00:06:50,709 --> 00:06:52,629
<Default><b>The same way
he gave me a home</b></Default>

117
00:06:53,250 --> 00:06:54,685
<Default><b>he gave each of you</b></Default>

118
00:06:54,709 --> 00:06:57,329
<Default><b>the wonderful country
of Siltvelt to call home.</b></Default>

119
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,720
<Default><b>It's so easy to forget.</b></Default>

120
00:07:00,829 --> 00:07:04,209
<Default><b>But we really do owe everything
we have to the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

121
00:07:04,709 --> 00:07:07,209
<Default><b>Everything we do</b></Default>

122
00:07:07,829 --> 00:07:09,935
<Default><b>Then it sounds like
we're in agreement.</b></Default>

123
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:11,999
<Default><b>We owe the Shield Hero
our lives.</b></Default>

124
00:07:12,170 --> 00:07:13,435
<Default><b>Does everyone concur?</b></Default>

125
00:07:13,459 --> 00:07:14,476
<Default><b>[CROWD] I concur.</b></Default>

126
00:07:14,500 --> 00:07:15,129
<Default><b>Yes!</b></Default>

127
00:07:15,250 --> 00:07:17,016
<Default><b>We're of
different countries</b></Default>

128
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:19,520
<Default><b>but the feelings that
we share are the same.</b></Default>

129
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:21,516
<Default><b>But our country
is much bigger</b></Default>

130
00:07:21,540 --> 00:07:23,620
<Default><b>than a tiny village
like your own.</b></Default>

131
00:07:23,709 --> 00:07:24,290
<Default><b>Tell me.</b></Default>

132
00:07:24,379 --> 00:07:27,539
<Default><b>Was it always that way here?
Or did you also start out small?</b></Default>

133
00:07:28,209 --> 00:07:30,646
<Default><b>[ATLA] Are you saying
the village Master Naofumi</b></Default>

134
00:07:30,670 --> 00:07:33,500
<Default><b>has brought back to life
is too small to matter?</b></Default>

135
00:07:33,579 --> 00:07:34,899
<Default><b>[MAN] No, but…</b></Default>

136
00:07:35,170 --> 00:07:37,305
<Default><b>But think about why
we have our power.</b></Default>

137
00:07:37,329 --> 00:07:38,250
<Default><b>Our claws.</b></Default>

138
00:07:38,329 --> 00:07:39,489
<Default><b>Our fangs.</b></Default>

139
00:07:40,079 --> 00:07:42,959
<Default><b>Is it to take from people
who can't defend themselves?</b></Default>

140
00:07:43,379 --> 00:07:45,516
<Default><b>[ATLA] Or to stand up
and protect them?</b></Default>

141
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:47,976
<Default><b>The answer lies
at the center of our being.</b></Default>

142
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,709
<Default><b>Well, it's because...</b></Default>

143
00:07:50,290 --> 00:07:51,646
<Default><b>You're not thinking!</b></Default>

144
00:07:51,670 --> 00:07:53,590
<Default><b>We have these
for one purpose.</b></Default>

145
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:55,510
<Default><b>To serve the
Shield Hero.</b></Default>

146
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:59,719
<Default><b>[ATLA] Even if you mock me
for having tainted blood</b></Default>

147
00:07:59,959 --> 00:08:01,839
<Default><b>the blood that
resides in me</b></Default>

148
00:08:02,079 --> 00:08:04,079
<Default><b>my heart, my soul.</b></Default>

149
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:06,420
<Default><b>Each of them
cries out to me</b></Default>

150
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:10,329
<Default><b>to express my undying loyalty
to the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

151
00:08:11,459 --> 00:08:14,579
<Default><b>[ATLA] The waves of calamity
you fear wait for no one.</b></Default>

152
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:17,400
<Default><b>Only the Shield Hero
can help us fight back.</b></Default>

153
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:20,226
<Default><b>[ATLA] We must not
forget who we serve.</b></Default>

154
00:08:20,250 --> 00:08:22,805
<Default><b>[MAN] She's right!
Only he can bring us together.</b></Default>

155
00:08:22,829 --> 00:08:25,920
<Default><b>[MAN] The man before us is
the hero of the time to come.</b></Default>

156
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:26,750
<Default><b>[murmurs]</b></Default>

157
00:08:26,829 --> 00:08:27,459
<Default><b>[deep exhale]</b></Default>

158
00:08:27,540 --> 00:08:29,580
<Default><b>[JARALIS] Disgusting
white tiger.</b></Default>

159
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:31,510
<Default><b>That was
certainly a lot.</b></Default>

160
00:08:31,579 --> 00:08:33,355
<Default><b>But none of it
sounded wrong</b></Default>

161
00:08:33,379 --> 00:08:35,976
<Default><b>so I don't know if there's
anything to add to it.</b></Default>

162
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,640
<Default><b>Right, Master Naofumi?</b></Default>

163
00:08:37,669 --> 00:08:38,330
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

164
00:08:38,629 --> 00:08:40,395
<Default><b>She's got a
way with words.</b></Default>

165
00:08:40,419 --> 00:08:41,976
<Default><b>[WERNER] Our
sole objective</b></Default>

166
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:44,879
<Default><b>is to support the Shield Hero
and do all that we can</b></Default>

167
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:47,419
<Default><b>to save the world
from the coming disaster.</b></Default>

168
00:08:47,710 --> 00:08:50,470
<Default><b>I'd like to thank you
for helping us remember that.</b></Default>

169
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:52,830
<Default><b>[WERNER] And yet</b></Default>

170
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:55,379
<Default><b>you would try and poison
the Shield Hero!</b></Default>

171
00:08:55,669 --> 00:08:57,589
<Default><b>What you did
is unforgivable.</b></Default>

172
00:08:57,629 --> 00:08:59,265
<Default><b>Give them the
death sentence!</b></Default>

173
00:08:59,289 --> 00:09:01,609
<Default><b>Why would you commit
such a heinous act?</b></Default>

174
00:09:01,879 --> 00:09:03,750
<Default><b>You dare
accuse us of that?</b></Default>

175
00:09:03,830 --> 00:09:06,186
<Default><b>Where's your proof
we did anything anyway?</b></Default>

176
00:09:06,210 --> 00:09:07,710
<Default><b>Filo, Sadeena!</b></Default>

177
00:09:08,710 --> 00:09:10,039
<Default><b>Don't worry!</b></Default>

178
00:09:10,129 --> 00:09:12,409
<Default><b>We made sure to bring him
here with us.</b></Default>

179
00:09:12,919 --> 00:09:14,830
<Default><b>Oh, hey there, Master.</b></Default>

180
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,160
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

181
00:09:16,210 --> 00:09:17,645
<Default><b>[♪ Suspense music]</b></Default>

182
00:09:17,669 --> 00:09:19,129
<Default><b>[murmurs]</b></Default>

183
00:09:19,289 --> 00:09:20,889
<Default><b>Right this way, dear.</b></Default>

184
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:22,040
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

185
00:09:22,250 --> 00:09:24,080
<Default><b>Hi. My name is Denny.</b></Default>

186
00:09:24,210 --> 00:09:26,015
<Default><b>I was the one
given the honor</b></Default>

187
00:09:26,039 --> 00:09:28,605
<Default><b>of preparing breakfast
for the Shield Hero today.</b></Default>

188
00:09:28,629 --> 00:09:31,509
<Default><b>I'm a court chef, so it
should've been smooth sailing.</b></Default>

189
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:34,790
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

190
00:09:38,250 --> 00:09:39,330
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

191
00:09:39,419 --> 00:09:40,459
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

192
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,400
<Default><b>I'm still hungry.</b></Default>

193
00:09:42,539 --> 00:09:44,699
<Default><b>Can we go back
to breakfast, Master?</b></Default>

194
00:09:45,210 --> 00:09:47,436
<Default><b>I don't mind eating it
if it's poisoned.</b></Default>

195
00:09:47,460 --> 00:09:50,260
<Default><b>Once we finish dealing
with stuff here, you can eat.</b></Default>

196
00:09:50,500 --> 00:09:51,500
<Default><b>Fine.</b></Default>

197
00:09:52,419 --> 00:09:53,515
<Default><b>Let me explain.</b></Default>

198
00:09:53,539 --> 00:09:54,895
<Default><b>Over the last three days</b></Default>

199
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:57,830
<Default><b>I've had Ethan keep an eye
on things in the palace.</b></Default>

200
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:00,250
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

201
00:10:00,379 --> 00:10:02,779
<Default><b>[MAN] A white tiger
working with the hero?</b></Default>

202
00:10:03,379 --> 00:10:05,436
<Default><b>The welcome was
more than enough to</b></Default>

203
00:10:05,460 --> 00:10:07,976
<Default><b>to make me suspect each
and every one of you.</b></Default>

204
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,226
<Default><b>While I was doing recon</b></Default>

205
00:10:09,250 --> 00:10:12,080
<Default><b>I saw him add poison
to today's breakfast.</b></Default>

206
00:10:12,710 --> 00:10:13,330
<Default><b>[sigh]</b></Default>

207
00:10:13,629 --> 00:10:14,976
<Default><b>You have to forgive me.</b></Default>

208
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,476
<Default><b>I swear, it wasn't me.</b></Default>

209
00:10:16,500 --> 00:10:17,000
<Default><b>It was…</b></Default>

210
00:10:17,330 --> 00:10:18,000
<Default><b>[sigh]</b></Default>

211
00:10:18,169 --> 00:10:19,476
<Default><b>I had to do it.</b></Default>

212
00:10:19,500 --> 00:10:20,645
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Don't worry.</b></Default>

213
00:10:20,669 --> 00:10:22,056
<Default><b>Your family is safe.</b></Default>

214
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:22,750
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

215
00:10:22,830 --> 00:10:24,476
<Default><b>You're free to
speak your mind.</b></Default>

216
00:10:24,500 --> 00:10:26,645
<Default><b>No harm will be coming
their way now.</b></Default>

217
00:10:26,669 --> 00:10:28,830
<Default><b>Oh, thank you,
Shield Hero.</b></Default>

218
00:10:29,330 --> 00:10:31,170
<Default><b>Who told you
to use poison?</b></Default>

219
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:32,700
<Default><b>[hesitates]</b></Default>

220
00:10:33,039 --> 00:10:34,079
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

221
00:10:35,330 --> 00:10:36,960
<Default><b>Jaralis told me to.</b></Default>

222
00:10:37,039 --> 00:10:37,539
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

223
00:10:37,629 --> 00:10:38,250
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

224
00:10:38,580 --> 00:10:39,620
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

225
00:10:40,460 --> 00:10:43,500
<Default><b>But I only did it because
he threatened me and my family.</b></Default>

226
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:46,145
<Default><b>Look, he's telling
the truth, Master.</b></Default>

227
00:10:46,169 --> 00:10:47,609
<Default><b>Explain yourself.</b></Default>

228
00:10:47,789 --> 00:10:48,789
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

229
00:10:49,789 --> 00:10:50,895
<Default><b>How strange.</b></Default>

230
00:10:50,919 --> 00:10:53,105
<Default><b>I don't believe you
and I have met before.</b></Default>

231
00:10:53,129 --> 00:10:55,529
<Default><b>Are you sure it was me
who instructed you?</b></Default>

232
00:10:55,710 --> 00:10:58,539
<Default><b>You weren't just given my name
to say at this time?</b></Default>

233
00:10:58,879 --> 00:11:00,079
<Default><b>Well, uh...</b></Default>

234
00:11:00,419 --> 00:11:01,645
<Default><b>Look, Shield Hero.</b></Default>

235
00:11:01,669 --> 00:11:04,879
<Default><b>I can only assume that this is
a plot to ruin my good name.</b></Default>

236
00:11:05,129 --> 00:11:07,329
<Default><b>I've yet to see
any proof I did this.</b></Default>

237
00:11:07,379 --> 00:11:10,145
<Default><b>Yeah, where's the proof?
There must be something, right?</b></Default>

238
00:11:10,169 --> 00:11:11,306
<Default><b>He is the proof!</b></Default>

239
00:11:11,330 --> 00:11:13,186
<Default><b>Just drop the
act and confess!</b></Default>

240
00:11:13,210 --> 00:11:14,930
<Default><b>{\i1}I figured he'd say that.{\i0}</b></Default>

241
00:11:15,169 --> 00:11:17,250
<Default><b>[people chattering
indistinctly]</b></Default>

242
00:11:21,830 --> 00:11:23,105
<Default><b>That's enough!</b></Default>

243
00:11:23,129 --> 00:11:24,306
<Default><b>Let's go, Filo.</b></Default>

244
00:11:24,330 --> 00:11:25,330
<Default><b>Okay.</b></Default>

245
00:11:25,379 --> 00:11:26,726
<Default><b>Well, either way</b></Default>

246
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:29,395
<Default><b>I'm not staying in a country
that tries to poison me.</b></Default>

247
00:11:29,419 --> 00:11:31,226
<Default><b>Deal with the
rest yourselves.</b></Default>

248
00:11:31,250 --> 00:11:32,169
<Default><b>Shield Hero!</b></Default>

249
00:11:32,250 --> 00:11:34,015
<Default><b>[JARALIS]
Before you leave.</b></Default>

250
00:11:34,039 --> 00:11:34,500
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

251
00:11:34,580 --> 00:11:37,620
<Default><b>There's something I think
everyone here should know about.</b></Default>

252
00:11:37,789 --> 00:11:39,830
<Default><b>I believe with
all my heart</b></Default>

253
00:11:39,919 --> 00:11:41,556
<Default><b>the Shield
Hero before us is</b></Default>

254
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:44,669
<Default><b>not the hero of the time to come
we've been waiting for.</b></Default>

255
00:11:44,750 --> 00:11:47,250
<Default><b>That's enough, Jaralis!
You go too far!</b></Default>

256
00:11:47,330 --> 00:11:49,789
<Default><b>Like all of you here</b></Default>

257
00:11:49,879 --> 00:11:52,726
<Default><b>for the future of Siltvelt
and want to see it prosper.</b></Default>

258
00:11:52,750 --> 00:11:55,879
<Default><b>Making the wrong decision could
spell the end for our nation</b></Default>

259
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,686
<Default><b>and that is why
I am now forced</b></Default>

260
00:11:57,710 --> 00:11:59,870
<Default><b>to speak up against
the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

261
00:11:59,919 --> 00:12:01,239
<Default><b>Master Naofumi</b></Default>

262
00:12:01,580 --> 00:12:04,789
<Default><b>our god, is not one
to make mistakes.</b></Default>

263
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,250
<Default><b>Raphy?</b></Default>

264
00:12:07,460 --> 00:12:08,210
<Default><b>Tell me then</b></Default>

265
00:12:08,419 --> 00:12:10,556
<Default><b>are you so foolish that
you would suggest</b></Default>

266
00:12:10,580 --> 00:12:12,355
<Default><b>he isn't the real
Shield Hero?</b></Default>

267
00:12:12,379 --> 00:12:14,299
<Default><b>Well, I wouldn't
go that far.</b></Default>

268
00:12:14,629 --> 00:12:15,169
<Default><b>However</b></Default>

269
00:12:15,379 --> 00:12:18,299
<Default><b>I want to call into question
if what we're experiencing</b></Default>

270
00:12:18,379 --> 00:12:20,379
<Default><b>truly are the
waves of calamity.</b></Default>

271
00:12:21,669 --> 00:12:24,789
<Default><b>If they really are meant
to destroy the whole world</b></Default>

272
00:12:24,919 --> 00:12:27,750
<Default><b>then why was the Shield Hero
summoned to Melromarc?</b></Default>

273
00:12:27,830 --> 00:12:30,460
<Default><b>And not the country
that worships him as a god?</b></Default>

274
00:12:32,289 --> 00:12:34,395
<Default><b>That fact alone is
all the proof you need</b></Default>

275
00:12:34,419 --> 00:12:37,099
<Default><b>to know he's not the hero
we've been waiting for.</b></Default>

276
00:12:37,169 --> 00:12:38,529
<Default><b>So I ask again!</b></Default>

277
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:41,039
<Default><b>Is he truly the hero
of the time to come?</b></Default>

278
00:12:41,129 --> 00:12:43,169
<Default><b>I believe it
remains to be seen.</b></Default>

279
00:12:44,539 --> 00:12:45,579
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

280
00:12:48,750 --> 00:12:49,539
<Default><b>[MAN] You mean…</b></Default>

281
00:12:49,669 --> 00:12:53,000
<Default><b>The Shield Hero isn't the hero
that we've been waiting for?</b></Default>

282
00:12:54,169 --> 00:12:55,645
<Default><b>I always have
found it odd</b></Default>

283
00:12:55,669 --> 00:12:58,069
<Default><b>that he was summoned
to Melromarc instead.</b></Default>

284
00:12:58,169 --> 00:12:59,710
<Default><b>{\i1}I get it now.{\i0}</b></Default>

285
00:12:59,879 --> 00:13:01,999
<Default><b>{\i1}So this is why{\i0}
{\i1}Jaralis was so calm.{\i0}</b></Default>

286
00:13:02,039 --> 00:13:03,519
<Default><b>[♪ Suspense music]</b></Default>

287
00:13:03,580 --> 00:13:05,476
<Default><b>The answer to
that is obvious.</b></Default>

288
00:13:05,500 --> 00:13:07,476
<Default><b>What we're facing now
are the waves.</b></Default>

289
00:13:07,500 --> 00:13:09,395
<Default><b>It's because of that
impending danger</b></Default>

290
00:13:09,419 --> 00:13:12,265
<Default><b>the Shield Hero was summoned
along with the other three.</b></Default>

291
00:13:12,289 --> 00:13:15,056
<Default><b>While each one of them
is powerful, their strength lies</b></Default>

292
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:16,936
<Default><b>in how they can
work together.</b></Default>

293
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:17,750
<Default><b>Because of that</b></Default>

294
00:13:17,830 --> 00:13:20,395
<Default><b>it only makes sense he was
summoned to Melromarc.</b></Default>

295
00:13:20,419 --> 00:13:23,259
<Default><b>It was his best chance to work
with the other heroes.</b></Default>

296
00:13:25,169 --> 00:13:28,009
<Default><b>That fact alone is proof
that the world is in danger.</b></Default>

297
00:13:28,129 --> 00:13:29,476
<Default><b>Sounds like nonsense.</b></Default>

298
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:30,765
<Default><b>I'm telling the truth.</b></Default>

299
00:13:30,789 --> 00:13:32,686
<Default><b>I'd expect anyone
who's sworn loyalty</b></Default>

300
00:13:32,710 --> 00:13:35,080
<Default><b>to Master Naofumi
to understand that.</b></Default>

301
00:13:35,169 --> 00:13:37,849
<Default><b>It seems I'm not the only one
who's sworn loyalty</b></Default>

302
00:13:37,879 --> 00:13:40,436
<Default><b>to him that holds doubt
for him in their hearts.</b></Default>

303
00:13:40,460 --> 00:13:41,500
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

304
00:13:42,289 --> 00:13:43,169
<Default><b>Err…</b></Default>

305
00:13:43,250 --> 00:13:44,290
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

306
00:13:45,419 --> 00:13:47,855
<Default><b>Didn't you all find it
to be a bit peculiar?</b></Default>

307
00:13:47,879 --> 00:13:50,539
<Default><b>If Werner had sworn loyalty
to the Shield Hero</b></Default>

308
00:13:50,629 --> 00:13:53,789
<Default><b>why hasn't he been able
to procure a ship as requested?</b></Default>

309
00:13:54,169 --> 00:13:57,056
<Default><b>[JARALIS] It's because if he
does not stay in the country</b></Default>

310
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:59,855
<Default><b>those who doubt that he is
the hero of the time to come</b></Default>

311
00:13:59,879 --> 00:14:01,519
<Default><b>will not be satisfied.</b></Default>

312
00:14:01,830 --> 00:14:03,030
<Default><b>Am I wrong?</b></Default>

313
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:05,240
<Default><b>It's just...</b></Default>

314
00:14:05,580 --> 00:14:07,220
<Default><b>You're all so selfish.</b></Default>

315
00:14:07,289 --> 00:14:07,960
<Default><b>Why?</b></Default>

316
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:10,460
<Default><b>After everything
Master Naofumi has done</b></Default>

317
00:14:10,539 --> 00:14:12,395
<Default><b>why do you insist
on prioritizing</b></Default>

318
00:14:12,419 --> 00:14:14,179
<Default><b>your own agendas
over him?</b></Default>

319
00:14:14,919 --> 00:14:17,419
<Default><b>I believe this girl's words
to be the truth.</b></Default>

320
00:14:17,789 --> 00:14:18,829
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

321
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:22,080
<Default><b>Young, but with a will
as strong as any.</b></Default>

322
00:14:22,379 --> 00:14:25,459
<Default><b>Weak in appearance, but fierce
in everything that she does.</b></Default>

323
00:14:26,500 --> 00:14:27,289
<Default><b>Look at her.</b></Default>

324
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:29,105
<Default><b>She might not
be from here</b></Default>

325
00:14:29,129 --> 00:14:31,960
<Default><b>but she exudes everything
our country stands for.</b></Default>

326
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:35,750
<Default><b>I believe her to be the only
true citizen of Siltvelt here.</b></Default>

327
00:14:36,500 --> 00:14:38,186
<Default><b>What are you doing here?</b></Default>

328
00:14:38,210 --> 00:14:39,210
<Default><b>Pff.</b></Default>

329
00:14:39,289 --> 00:14:41,395
<Default><b>[MAN] I can't believe
you really came.</b></Default>

330
00:14:41,419 --> 00:14:42,659
<Default><b>Who is this?</b></Default>

331
00:14:42,830 --> 00:14:44,710
<Default><b>[WERNER] The
Elder of Genmu.</b></Default>

332
00:14:44,789 --> 00:14:47,039
<Default><b>He's been retired
for some time now.</b></Default>

333
00:14:47,379 --> 00:14:48,080
<Default><b>Despite that</b></Default>

334
00:14:48,169 --> 00:14:51,289
<Default><b>he holds a lot of influence
with all the different factions.</b></Default>

335
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,789
<Default><b>[♪ Smooth music]</b></Default>

336
00:14:54,830 --> 00:14:57,080
<Default><b>It's an honor
to meet you</b></Default>

337
00:14:57,169 --> 00:15:00,210
<Default><b>I never thought the day would
come you'd stand before me.</b></Default>

338
00:15:00,500 --> 00:15:01,960
<Default><b>I'm Elder Genmu.</b></Default>

339
00:15:02,039 --> 00:15:04,799
<Default><b>But you can call me Elder
if it's too much trouble.</b></Default>

340
00:15:05,210 --> 00:15:07,289
<Default><b>Elder, your appearance.</b></Default>

341
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:09,919
<Default><b>You do stand before
the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

342
00:15:10,169 --> 00:15:12,000
<Default><b>Ah, yes, my apologies.</b></Default>

343
00:15:12,250 --> 00:15:14,556
<Default><b>Understand, it's required
I take this form</b></Default>

344
00:15:14,580 --> 00:15:16,879
<Default><b>in order to better
protect myself.</b></Default>

345
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,920
<Default><b>It's practically
a habit now.</b></Default>

346
00:15:21,039 --> 00:15:22,395
<Default><b>[vibrant sound]</b></Default>

347
00:15:22,419 --> 00:15:25,500
<Default><b>I didn't mean
to eavesdrop</b></Default>

348
00:15:26,669 --> 00:15:30,129
<Default><b>Does anyone here disagree with
anything this girl said earlier?</b></Default>

349
00:15:30,419 --> 00:15:32,556
<Default><b>How could you
when she speaks the truth?</b></Default>

350
00:15:32,580 --> 00:15:35,420
<Default><b>It's utter foolishness to
prioritize your own desires</b></Default>

351
00:15:35,500 --> 00:15:39,039
<Default><b>over those of the Shield Hero
who now stands before us.</b></Default>

352
00:15:39,129 --> 00:15:40,806
<Default><b>The Elder's
absolutely right.</b></Default>

353
00:15:40,830 --> 00:15:44,015
<Default><b>So you would listen to the words
of someone with tainted blood?</b></Default>

354
00:15:44,039 --> 00:15:47,250
<Default><b>No true citizen of Siltvelt
would ever do such a thing.</b></Default>

355
00:15:47,580 --> 00:15:49,060
<Default><b>I've heard enough.</b></Default>

356
00:15:50,039 --> 00:15:51,726
<Default><b>If you insist
on continuing to be</b></Default>

357
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:54,539
<Default><b>an obstacle for Master
Naofumi's endeavors</b></Default>

358
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:57,750
<Default><b>then I shall
eliminate you by force.</b></Default>

359
00:15:58,210 --> 00:15:58,879
<Default><b>Atla!</b></Default>

360
00:15:59,000 --> 00:15:59,750
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

361
00:15:59,830 --> 00:16:01,605
<Default><b>If it's a death wish
you have</b></Default>

362
00:16:01,629 --> 00:16:05,000
<Default><b>I'll kill you and stain my hands
with your cursed blood.</b></Default>

363
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:06,800
<Default><b>I accept your challenge.</b></Default>

364
00:16:07,039 --> 00:16:08,639
<Default><b>Silence, both of you.</b></Default>

365
00:16:09,710 --> 00:16:10,790
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

366
00:16:11,379 --> 00:16:12,499
<Default><b>[disdain]</b></Default>

367
00:16:12,750 --> 00:16:16,129
<Default><b>Yelling at each other isn't
going to do anyone any good.</b></Default>

368
00:16:16,539 --> 00:16:18,460
<Default><b>Now let's see
what to do.</b></Default>

369
00:16:18,789 --> 00:16:19,460
<Default><b>Ah!</b></Default>

370
00:16:19,539 --> 00:16:22,210
<Default><b>As is Siltvelt tradition
to do so</b></Default>

371
00:16:22,289 --> 00:16:24,515
<Default><b>why don't we settle things
with a duel?</b></Default>

372
00:16:24,539 --> 00:16:25,750
<Default><b>[murmurs]</b></Default>

373
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:27,120
<Default><b>A duel?</b></Default>

374
00:16:27,460 --> 00:16:28,080
<Default><b>Elder!</b></Default>

375
00:16:28,210 --> 00:16:30,129
<Default><b>Is that not
a bit too far?</b></Default>

376
00:16:30,460 --> 00:16:34,460
<Default><b>If there is doubt that he is
the hero of the time to come</b></Default>

377
00:16:34,539 --> 00:16:36,015
<Default><b>then this must
come to pass.</b></Default>

378
00:16:36,039 --> 00:16:39,000
<Default><b>If it didn't happen now</b></Default>

379
00:16:39,500 --> 00:16:40,540
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

380
00:16:41,210 --> 00:16:42,476
<Default><b>If you say so.</b></Default>

381
00:16:42,500 --> 00:16:43,895
<Default><b>Well, in that case</b></Default>

382
00:16:43,919 --> 00:16:45,806
<Default><b>I volunteer to serve
as second</b></Default>

383
00:16:45,830 --> 00:16:48,210
<Default><b>to the white tiger
Demi-human, that is.</b></Default>

384
00:16:48,289 --> 00:16:48,879
<Default><b>Jaralis!</b></Default>

385
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:51,976
<Default><b>[WERNER] If you intend to prove
what you believe to be true</b></Default>

386
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,920
<Default><b>then you must
accept the duel.</b></Default>

387
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,040
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

388
00:16:56,500 --> 00:17:00,169
<Default><b>For the sake
of what is fair</b></Default>

389
00:17:00,669 --> 00:17:03,539
<Default><b>I hope someone
of my stature is up to par.</b></Default>

390
00:17:03,830 --> 00:17:06,039
<Default><b>Are these terms
satisfactory for you?</b></Default>

391
00:17:06,289 --> 00:17:08,646
<Default><b>After all the lies
you've spoken till now</b></Default>

392
00:17:08,670 --> 00:17:11,186
<Default><b>I'm sure you're willing to take
the risk of what</b></Default>

393
00:17:11,210 --> 00:17:14,330
<Default><b>will happen if you find yourself
on the losing side of this.</b></Default>

394
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:15,860
<Default><b>Of course I am.</b></Default>

395
00:17:16,210 --> 00:17:16,880
<Default><b>Ha!</b></Default>

396
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:18,960
<Default><b>I accept the terms
of this duel.</b></Default>

397
00:17:19,039 --> 00:17:20,319
<Default><b>[crowd gasps]</b></Default>

398
00:17:20,630 --> 00:17:23,030
<Default><b>This whole situation's
gotten out of hand.</b></Default>

399
00:17:23,130 --> 00:17:24,130
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

400
00:17:24,579 --> 00:17:27,829
<Default><b>{\i1}I thought the poison would be my{\i0}
{\i1}trump card to get to Q'ten Lo.{\i0}</b></Default>

401
00:17:28,289 --> 00:17:30,289
<Default><b>{\i1}So why are we having{\i0}
{\i1}a duel now?{\i0}</b></Default>

402
00:17:31,130 --> 00:17:33,250
<Default><b>Now, if I win
this little duel…</b></Default>

403
00:17:33,710 --> 00:17:34,500
<Default><b>[JARALIS] First</b></Default>

404
00:17:34,579 --> 00:17:36,726
<Default><b>we shall strip the white
tiger Demi-humans</b></Default>

405
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:39,910
<Default><b>of their position as one of the
four great races in Siltvelt.</b></Default>

406
00:17:40,079 --> 00:17:43,130
<Default><b>And in their place, we Laio
shall rise to power.</b></Default>

407
00:17:43,210 --> 00:17:44,290
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

408
00:17:44,460 --> 00:17:47,396
<Default><b>Furthermore, the Shield Hero
shall belong to our country</b></Default>

409
00:17:47,420 --> 00:17:49,060
<Default><b>and our country alone.</b></Default>

410
00:17:50,170 --> 00:17:53,920
<Default><b>Finally, the girl with tainted
blood shall face punishment.</b></Default>

411
00:17:54,039 --> 00:17:56,055
<Default><b>[JARALIS] Are these terms
okay with you?</b></Default>

412
00:17:56,079 --> 00:17:59,106
<Default><b>Hell no! The results of the duel
are weighted in your favor.</b></Default>

413
00:17:59,130 --> 00:18:00,356
<Default><b>Sounds good to me.</b></Default>

414
00:18:00,380 --> 00:18:03,420
<Default><b>You needn't
worry. If I win</b></Default>

415
00:18:05,210 --> 00:18:06,330
<Default><b>So be it.</b></Default>

416
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:10,420
<Default><b>Well, if I win the duel, you're
to do whatever I want, Jaralis.</b></Default>

417
00:18:10,630 --> 00:18:12,670
<Default><b>It would be my pleasure</b></Default>

418
00:18:12,750 --> 00:18:15,310
<Default><b>However, I don't think
that will be happening.</b></Default>

419
00:18:15,380 --> 00:18:16,420
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

420
00:18:17,210 --> 00:18:17,789
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

421
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,646
<Default><b>If the Shield
Hero's party wins</b></Default>

422
00:18:19,670 --> 00:18:22,380
<Default><b>Siltvelt will grant
whatever your heart desires.</b></Default>

423
00:18:22,710 --> 00:18:24,186
<Default><b>Is that satisfactory?</b></Default>

424
00:18:24,210 --> 00:18:25,410
<Default><b>Fine by me.</b></Default>

425
00:18:26,670 --> 00:18:28,515
<Default><b>Very well.
I permit this duel.</b></Default>

426
00:18:28,539 --> 00:18:30,765
<Default><b>The white tiger Demi-human
versus Jaralis.</b></Default>

427
00:18:30,789 --> 00:18:31,420
<Default><b>Hold on.</b></Default>

428
00:18:31,500 --> 00:18:32,000
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

429
00:18:32,420 --> 00:18:33,646
<Default><b>Brother, please.</b></Default>

430
00:18:33,670 --> 00:18:36,039
<Default><b>Let me fight.
I can take her place.</b></Default>

431
00:18:36,630 --> 00:18:38,150
<Default><b>I should be the one</b></Default>

432
00:18:38,380 --> 00:18:40,060
<Default><b>to defeat that monster!</b></Default>

433
00:18:41,500 --> 00:18:42,500
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

434
00:18:43,130 --> 00:18:44,650
<Default><b>I can't allow that.</b></Default>

435
00:18:44,750 --> 00:18:47,079
<Default><b>Master Naofumi's future
is at stake</b></Default>

436
00:18:47,170 --> 00:18:49,436
<Default><b>and I can't trust you
to win this duel.</b></Default>

437
00:18:49,460 --> 00:18:50,079
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

438
00:18:50,250 --> 00:18:51,370
<Default><b>Atla dear</b></Default>

439
00:18:51,420 --> 00:18:53,220
<Default><b>why not give
him a chance?</b></Default>

440
00:18:53,250 --> 00:18:55,650
<Default><b>After all, I've never
seen him so certain.</b></Default>

441
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:57,320
<Default><b>I know, but...</b></Default>

442
00:18:57,539 --> 00:18:59,960
<Default><b>There's something
I have to ask him, Atla.</b></Default>

443
00:19:00,579 --> 00:19:02,659
<Default><b>And I'll do it
after I defeat him.</b></Default>

444
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:04,400
<Default><b>It has to be me.</b></Default>

445
00:19:06,210 --> 00:19:08,289
<Default><b>I'll beat him for
me and Father.</b></Default>

446
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:09,380
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

447
00:19:09,880 --> 00:19:12,329
<Default><b>If you're so determined</b></Default>

448
00:19:12,670 --> 00:19:14,055
<Default><b>[exhales nervously]</b></Default>

449
00:19:14,079 --> 00:19:15,856
<Default><b>Nothing would
make me happier</b></Default>

450
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:19,079
<Default><b>than to show you what noble
blood is capable of doing.</b></Default>

451
00:19:20,539 --> 00:19:21,726
<Default><b>Don't be daft.</b></Default>

452
00:19:21,750 --> 00:19:25,079
<Default><b>Duels must be fought with equal
participants on either side.</b></Default>

453
00:19:25,170 --> 00:19:27,055
<Default><b>Yes, you needn't
worry though.</b></Default>

454
00:19:27,079 --> 00:19:29,159
<Default><b>I'll happily bring
another person.</b></Default>

455
00:19:29,380 --> 00:19:31,329
<Default><b>Is that all
right with you</b></Default>

456
00:19:31,630 --> 00:19:32,670
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

457
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:34,040
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

458
00:19:34,289 --> 00:19:36,829
<Default><b>Master Naofumi</b></Default>

459
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,856
<Default><b>Even if my
brother does fail</b></Default>

460
00:19:38,880 --> 00:19:40,960
<Default><b>I'm able to defeat them
on my own.</b></Default>

461
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:42,789
<Default><b>Atla, have faith in me!</b></Default>

462
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:45,055
<Default><b>[ATLA] Going along
with the enemy's plan</b></Default>

463
00:19:45,079 --> 00:19:47,420
<Default><b>and still winning
is a sign of strength.</b></Default>

464
00:19:47,500 --> 00:19:49,220
<Default><b>I promise you, I'll win.</b></Default>

465
00:19:49,289 --> 00:19:51,186
<Default><b>Please agree,
Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

466
00:19:51,210 --> 00:19:52,290
<Default><b>Come on.</b></Default>

467
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:55,040
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

468
00:19:56,329 --> 00:19:58,049
<Default><b>If that's what you want.</b></Default>

469
00:19:58,130 --> 00:19:59,226
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

470
00:19:59,250 --> 00:20:01,920
<Default><b>[♪ Smooth music]</b></Default>

471
00:20:09,079 --> 00:20:10,000
<Default><b>Raphy, Ra-Raphy!</b></Default>

472
00:20:10,079 --> 00:20:11,719
<Default><b>[ATLA] Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

473
00:20:12,539 --> 00:20:14,396
<Default><b>Are you positive
about this?</b></Default>

474
00:20:14,420 --> 00:20:17,670
<Default><b>I am, and it feels like it's
important to my brother too.</b></Default>

475
00:20:18,710 --> 00:20:22,460
<Default><b>This is my chance to prove how
strong my loyalty is for you.</b></Default>

476
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:26,250
<Default><b>Nothing makes me happier than
you knowing you can rely on me.</b></Default>

477
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:28,110
<Default><b>Above all else.</b></Default>

478
00:20:28,380 --> 00:20:30,880
<Default><b>I can't exactly
call myself your shield</b></Default>

479
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:33,040
<Default><b>if I can't overcome
a little duel.</b></Default>

480
00:20:33,380 --> 00:20:33,920
<Default><b>[approval]</b></Default>

481
00:20:34,250 --> 00:20:35,810
<Default><b>I'm counting on you.</b></Default>

482
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:37,250
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

483
00:20:37,329 --> 00:20:39,489
<Default><b>That's all I've ever
wanted to hear.</b></Default>

484
00:20:39,670 --> 00:20:41,250
<Default><b>[MAN] Both parties</b></Default>

485
00:20:41,829 --> 00:20:43,920
<Default><b>[♪ dramatic music]</b></Default>

486
00:20:44,789 --> 00:20:45,829
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

487
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:46,960
<Default><b>Hold on.</b></Default>

488
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:49,120
<Default><b>Who the hell is
that buff minotaur?</b></Default>

489
00:20:50,420 --> 00:20:51,130
<Default><b>Oh my.</b></Default>

490
00:20:51,380 --> 00:20:52,580
<Default><b>Incredible.</b></Default>

491
00:20:53,210 --> 00:20:54,646
<Default><b>He's called one
of the heroes</b></Default>

492
00:20:54,670 --> 00:20:57,579
<Default><b>from the last Great War
to fight alongside him.</b></Default>

493
00:20:58,039 --> 00:20:58,920
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

494
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:02,000
<Default><b>Seeing how this battle will
decide the Shield Hero's fate</b></Default>

495
00:21:02,079 --> 00:21:03,726
<Default><b>it would be foolish
to entrust</b></Default>

496
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:06,000
<Default><b>such a matter to anyone
but the best.</b></Default>

497
00:21:06,329 --> 00:21:07,649
<Default><b>Mark my words.</b></Default>

498
00:21:08,039 --> 00:21:09,670
<Default><b>I will be victorious.</b></Default>

499
00:21:10,329 --> 00:21:13,210
<Default><b>And my daughter shall marry
the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

500
00:21:13,500 --> 00:21:14,540
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

501
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:16,720
<Default><b>That wasn't a condition.</b></Default>

502
00:21:19,420 --> 00:21:20,896
<Default><b>[glimmering] [smirk]</b></Default>

503
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:22,015
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

504
00:21:22,039 --> 00:21:23,079
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

505
00:21:23,539 --> 00:21:27,289
<Default><b>How dare you use Master Naofumi
in your arranged marriage?</b></Default>

506
00:21:27,380 --> 00:21:28,750
<Default><b>Atla! Fohl!</b></Default>

507
00:21:28,829 --> 00:21:30,146
<Default><b>You have to win!</b></Default>

508
00:21:30,170 --> 00:21:31,436
<Default><b>Just leave it to us.</b></Default>

509
00:21:31,460 --> 00:21:32,039
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

510
00:21:32,380 --> 00:21:34,710
<Default><b>Jaralis, your
fight is with me.</b></Default>

511
00:21:35,380 --> 00:21:36,555
<Default><b>And if I win</b></Default>

512
00:21:36,579 --> 00:21:39,539
<Default><b>you have to tell me everything
you know about my dad.</b></Default>

513
00:21:39,960 --> 00:21:40,630
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

514
00:21:40,829 --> 00:21:42,710
<Default><b>Happily, filthy
white tiger.</b></Default>

515
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:49,420
<Default><b>Before we start the duel</b></Default>

516
00:21:50,329 --> 00:21:54,789
<Default><b>[♪ epic music]</b></Default>

517
00:21:59,500 --> 00:22:00,726
<Default><b>[MAN] Begin!</b></Default>

518
00:22:00,750 --> 00:22:02,039
<Default><b>[gong]</b></Default>

519
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:08,000
<Default><b>[♪ Closing music begins]</b></Default>

520
00:23:33,289 --> 00:23:35,329
<Default><b>[♪ Closing music ends]</b></Default>

521
00:23:36,289 --> 00:23:40,329
<Default><b>ENTRUSTED POWER</b></Default>

